{"tid":1167503,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【今日生日】孖老公撐枱腳預祝生日 吳若希：第三年慶祝我25歲生日","createTime":"2019-05-23T05:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T03:28:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cade67873b9cadce2103fa38b7d1f6d88dc7c042","tid":1167503,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"吳若希（Jinny）上個月剛剛為囡囡Giselle（淼淼）慶祝兩歲生日，今日就是她27歲生日喇！Jinny昨晚在IG貼出和老公Alex在家打邊爐慶祝生日的相片，Jinny還留言：「開開心心又一日，輕輕鬆鬆又一年，第三年慶祝我25歲生日，希望我愛的人和愛我的人繼續健康快樂。」<br />\n雖然在家簡簡單單慶祝，但Alex亦好識做，「禮物孖寶」鮮花加蛋糕當然唔會缺少，捧着蛋糕的Jinny被老公輕輕攬着纖腰拍照，笑容更加是甜到漏。<br />\n而這些大日子，兩公婆又再次夾攻強吻囡囡左右面頰，搞到囡囡瞇晒眼，一副完全唔知發生甚麼事的樣子，相當搞笑。Jinny代囡囡留言：「點解唔係我生日都要啜我。」其實Jinny兩日前已經開始慶祝生日，除了吃過壽包，昨日亦和兩位曾拍檔主持節目的莊思敏及葉翠翠食飯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190523/large/1558581594_aeb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190523%2Flarge%2F1558581594_aeb0.jpg&h=f0e6009e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190523/large/1558581596_bdba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190523%2Flarge%2F1558581596_bdba.jpg&h=7f164bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190523/large/1558581597_f64d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190523%2Flarge%2F1558581597_f64d.jpg&h=e6108158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190523/large/1558581597_3c32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190523%2Flarge%2F1558581597_3c32.jpg&h=47ec2aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190523/59631738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F59631738&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=3ae3d842\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F59631738&h=c7a8edaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190523/59631738</a>"},{"pid":"d745ec5328259312f19173ed92de570385935e78","tid":1167503,"uid":52194,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:28:30.000Z","msg":"人地25歲可以食飽飲醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我25歲仲日日為晏就嗰$三廿蚊頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ffcb3bc4647c692bdadc66973adf0ab2110aa7","tid":1167503,"uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d745ec5328259312f19173ed92de570385935e78","tid":1167503,"uid":52194,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:28:30.000Z","msg":"人地25歲可以食飽飲醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我25歲仲日日為晏就嗰$三廿蚊頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T23:46:55.000Z","msg":"條女仲要無學識無歌藝，呢個世界真係唔公平"},{"pid":"918e1c2b988739a47c810e88d4cd24af014de94a","tid":1167503,"uid":91238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T00:38:48.000Z","msg":"家門不幸"},{"pid":"03d5c886f6c8d14dca5c0b3cc9bc13efd71ed90b","tid":1167503,"uid":50041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:28:50.000Z","msg":"其實Jinny兩日前已經開始慶祝生日，除了吃過壽包，昨日亦和兩位曾拍檔主持節目的莊思敏及葉翠翠食飯。<br />\n<br />\n物以類聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}